<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Model on OWASP SAMM</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resource_tags/model/</link><description>Recent content in Model on OWASP SAMM</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://owaspsamm.org/resource_tags/model/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SAMM assessment tools</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/assessment-tools/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/assessment-tools/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="links-to-info-and-tools"&gt;Links to info and tools&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to learn more about SAMM assessments, we have a couple of dedicated pages for that. First, there&amp;rsquo;s the &lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.org/assessment/"&gt;assessment&lt;/a&gt; page. We also have an &lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.org/assessment-guide/"&gt;assessment guide&lt;/a&gt;, with lots of practical advice, best practices, and an &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rUsktgsGna65KJPCT91UiOxFRvKdFs0TJxCWN0aa5u4/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;example set of questions&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 for an interview-style assessment. If you&amp;rsquo;re just looking for the links to our spreadsheets or online assessment, here they are.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="spreadsheets"&gt;Spreadsheets&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have 2 versions of the SAMM Toolbox, a &lt;a href="https://github.com/owaspsamm/core/releases/latest" target="_blank"&gt;Microsoft Excel Toolbox&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 and a &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jmLVltRhuG19AX5cLUcWH1Qox2Uic17rD29gMVG5zDE/view#gid=1716553355" target="_blank"&gt;Google Spreadsheet Toolbox&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Training</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/training/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/training/</guid><description>&lt;img class="text-wrap-img-left" src="https://owaspsamm.org/img/resources/Fundamentals_Course.png" alt="SAMM Fundamentals Course"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A fully free, self-paced course with over 5 hours of video content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Visit the &lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.thinkific.com/courses/samm" target="_blank"&gt;SAMM Fundamentals Course page&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 on Thinkific.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;d really appreciate feedback on this first version of the course. Please use our &lt;a href="https://owasp.slack.com/archives/C0VF1EJGH" target="_blank"&gt;Slack channel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

, the &lt;a href="https://github.com/orgs/owaspsamm/discussions/" target="_blank"&gt;Discussions&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 on GitHub or our &lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.org/contact/"&gt;contact form&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SAMM Mappings</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/mappings/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/mappings/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="direct-mappings"&gt;Direct Mappings&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="mapping-between-microsoft-sdl-and-samm"&gt;Mapping between Microsoft SDL and SAMM&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SAMM core team has created mappings between Microsoft SDL and OWASP SAMM. You can find the mapping in &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1WiQcn7wFzSM8xg78SqkIM1QF2C48jBCYi_N_6kOq174" target="_blank"&gt;this spreadsheet&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can also find more information about this mapping in the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.org/blog/2025/01/20/comparing-microsoft-sdl-and-samm/"&gt;Microsoft SDL and OWASP SAMM Mapping: A Comprehensive Analysis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; blog post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="mapping-between-bsimm-14-and-samm"&gt;Mapping between BSIMM 14 and SAMM&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SAMM core team has created mappings between BSIMM 14 and OWASP SAMM standards. You can find the mapping in &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1WiQcn7wFzSM8xg78SqkIM1QF2C48jBCYi_N_6kOq174" target="_blank"&gt;this spreadsheet&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SAMM PDF</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/pdf/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/pdf/</guid><description>&lt;img class="text-wrap-img-left" src="https://owaspsamm.org/img/resources/PDF_file_icon.svg.png" alt="PDF icon"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a long awaited moment since the release of SAMM version 2. The community asked for it so we&amp;rsquo;ve created a PDF version of the model.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;View the SAMM PDF &lt;a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cI3Qzfrly_X89z7StLWI5p_Jfqs0-OZv/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any feedback on this, please use our &lt;a href="https://owasp.slack.com/archives/C0VF1EJGH" target="_blank"&gt;Slack channel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

, the &lt;a href="https://github.com/orgs/owaspsamm/discussions/" target="_blank"&gt;Discussions&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 on GitHub or our &lt;a href="https://owaspsamm.org/contact/"&gt;contact form&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SAMM GitHub repositories</title><link>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/github/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://owaspsamm.org/resources/github/</guid><description>&lt;img class="text-wrap-img-left" src="https://owaspsamm.org/img/resources/Octocat.png" alt="GitHub logo"&gt;

&lt;h2 id="one-project-many-repos"&gt;One project, many repos&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After the release of SAMM v2, we moved all of our GitHub content to the &lt;a href="https://github.com/owaspsamm" target="_blank"&gt;OWASP SAMM GitHub organization&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

. Here, you can find all the repositories related to the SAMM project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some of the repos you can find there are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/owaspsamm/core" target="_blank"&gt;Core Model&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/owaspsamm/website" target="_blank"&gt;Website&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/owaspsamm/sammwise" target="_blank"&gt;SAMMwise (assessment tool)&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, don&amp;rsquo;t miss the &lt;a href="https://github.com/orgs/owaspsamm/discussions/" target="_blank"&gt;Discussions&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i class="link-icon fas fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

 section, where you can pitch your ideas, ask questions, and provide feedback.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>